<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>TipStack Account Verification</title>
  <style>
    /* Reset styles */
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      color: #4a5568;
      line-height: 1.7;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    }

    .container {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 20px auto;
      background: linear-gradient(145deg, #ffffff 0%, #f8fafc 100%);
      border-radius: 16px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .header {
      text-align: center;
      color: #ffffff;
    }

    .brand-name {
      font-size: 42px;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -0.025em;
      color:rgba(6, 2, 75, 0.3)
    }

    .header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: -0.025em;
    }

    .body {
      padding: 40px 32px;
      text-align: left;
      background-color: #ffffff;
    }

    .body p {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #4a5568;
    }

    .verification-button {
      display: inline-block;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4f46e5 0%, #6366f1 100%);
      color: #ffffff !important;
      padding: 16px 32px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      text-decoration: none;
      margin: 32px 0;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 16px;
      text-align: center;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.2);
    }

    .verification-button:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.3);
    }

    .info-box {
      background: linear-gradient(145deg, #f8fafc 0%, #f1f5f9 100%);
      border-left: 4px solid #6366f1;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin: 24px 0;
    }

    .footer {
      background: linear-gradient(145deg, #f8fafc 0%, #f1f5f9 100%);
      text-align: center;
      padding: 32px;
      border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    }

    .footer p {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #64748b;
    }

    .footer a {
      color: #4f46e5;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 500;
      transition: color 0.2s ease;
    }

    .footer a:hover {
      color: #6366f1;
    }

    .social-links {
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .social-links a {
      margin: 0 8px;
      color: #64748b;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    /* Responsive Design */
    @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
      .container {
        margin: 10px;
        border-radius: 12px;
      }

      .header {
        padding: 32px 20px;
      }

      .brand-name {
        font-size: 36px;
      }

      .body {
        padding: 32px 20px;
      }

      .header h1 {
        font-size: 24px;
      }

      .verification-button {
        padding: 14px 28px;
        font-size: 15px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <div class="brand-name">TipStack</div>
      <h1>Verify Your Account</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="body">
      <p class="greeting">Hello ðŸ™Œ</p>
      <p>Welcome to TipStack! To ensure the security of your account and start sending tips, please verify your email
        address using the code below:</p>

      <div style="text-align: center; font-size: larger; font-weight: bold; color: indigo;">
        <%= activationCode %> 
      </div>

      <p style="margin-top: 24px;">This verification code will expire in 30 minutes. If you did not create a TipStack
        account, please disregard this email.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>Need help? Contact us at <a href="mailto:support@tipstack.com">support@tipstack.com</a></p>
      <div class="social-links">
        <a href="#">Twitter</a> â€¢
        <a href="#">Discord</a> â€¢
        <a href="#">Telegram</a>
      </div>
      <p style="margin-top: 20px;">Â© 2024 TipStack. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>